name: plplot
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "plplot" %}
{% set version = "5.15.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b92de4d8f626a9b20c84fc94f4f6a9976edd76e33fb1eae44f6804bdcc628c7b

build:
  number: 0
  script:
    - set -ex  # [unix]
    - CMAKE_ARGS=${CMAKE_ARGS//-DCMAKE_INSTALL_LIBDIR=lib/}  # [unix]
    - >
       cmake
       ${CMAKE_ARGS}  # [unix]
       -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=%LIBRARY_PREFIX%  # [win]
       -DENABLE_octave=OFF
       -DENABLE_tcl=ON
       -DENABLE_tk=ON
       -DBUILD_TEST=ON
       -B_build
       -GNinja
    - cmake --build _build
    - ctest --test-dir _build  # [build_platform == target_platform]
    - cmake --install _build

  run_exports:
    - {{ pin_subpackage(name, max_pin='x') }}

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}  # [unix]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}  # [unix]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}  # [unix]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}  # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}  # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}  # [win]
    - cmake
    - ninja
    - pkg-config
  host:
    - tk
  run:
    - tk

test:
  requires:
    - pkg-config
  commands:
    - pkg-config --exact-version {{ version }} {{ name }}
    - pkg-config --exact-version {{ version }} {{ name }}-tcl
    - pkg-config --exact-version {{ version }} {{ name }}-fortran
    - pkg-config --exact-version {{ version }} {{ name }}-c++

about:
  home: http://plplot.sourceforge.net
  license: LGPL-2.0-or-later
  license_file: Copyright
  summary: A cross-platform software package for creating scientific plots

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - awvwgk
